General Information - Enlisted MOS Conversion List (Air Force)

Click the Warrant Officer MOSs below to see the duty description, prerequisites, and preferred qualifications that you may be eligible to apply for. Please remember, you must meet the MINIMUM prerequisites for the Warrant Officer MOS for which you will apply, or you must request a prerequisite waiver.

Waivers are not needed for preferred qualifications.

Basic qualifications to apply to become a Warrant Officer in the United States Army

AVAILABLE TO INTERESTED APPLICANTS, NO FEEDER JOB REQUIRED

153A - Rotary Wing Aviator

170A - Cyber Warfare Technician

170D - Cyber Capabilities Developer Technician

255A - Information Systems Technician

255N - Network Systems Technician

270A - Legal Administrator
